****************************************
**  Social Network Library - Twitter  **
****************************************

URL:        https://github.com/thibauthavel/FreeRTOS-Social-Network-Library
Author:     Thibaut Havel, Teesside University, UK (L1247434)



Content
-------
* FreeRTOS_Posix:   The FreeRTOS POSIX simulator contening the libtwitter library.
* libtwitter:       A copy of the two main files of the library (libtwitter.c and libtwitter.h).
* Documentation:    A HTML documentation of the tow main files generated by Doxygen.
* Report:           LaTeX source code and the PDF version of the report.



FreeRTOS POSIX simulator
------------------------
To test a working version of the library via a FreeRTOS POSIX simulator:
* OpenSSL and libcurl should be installed in your UNIX system.
* cd FreeRTOS_Posix/Debug/
* make clean; make all
* ./FreeRTOS_Posix



